라~♪ㅋ... blog.naver.com본문으로 이동 ﻿ 도움이 되셨나요? 따뜻한 덧글,소중한 공감 하나로 흔적을 남겨주세요-♡ ​ ﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿보시고 담아가시는 데는 잠시 잠깐이시지만,  포스팅을 하기까진 제법 오랜 시간이 걸린답니다. 기본적인 매너는 지켜주세요-!     *삶에 희망을 더해가는 아마로니의 희망플러스* ﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿","images":["http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141201_193/saakrang80_1417403583449OKXbH_JPEG/IMG_5376.png?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141201_174/saakrang80_14174035868661AGaV_JPEG/IMG_5389.png?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141201_252/saakrang80_1417403587627RjGeW_JPEG/IMG_5044.png?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141201_141/saakrang80_1417404339681fCOQP_PNG/%BA%EA%B7%CE%C4%DD%B8%AE.PNG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141201_37/saakrang80_1417403588533XhxHs_JPEG/IMG_5053.png?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141201_181/saakrang80_1417404369102a7UDG_PNG/%BA%EA%B7%CE%C4%DD%B8%AE1.PNG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141201_185/saakrang80_1417403596099TqUyb_JPEG/IMG_5063.png?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141201_103/saakrang80_1417404432072v6kpI_PNG/%BA%EA%B7%CE%C4%DD%B8%AE2.PNG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141201_79/saakrang80_1417413390511MW9Dc_PNG/%BA%EA%B7%CE%C4%DD%B8%AE4.PNG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141201_50/saakrang80_1417403598040dRaGx_JPEG/IMG_5068.png?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141201_201/saakrang80_1417403599244jeCD4_JPEG/IMG_5379.png?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141201_247/saakrang80_14174035998853Fp7k_JPEG/IMG_5380.png?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141201_191/saakrang80_1417403600325ydHqz_JPEG/IMG_5394.png?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141201_15/saakrang80_1417413816933LDFb0_GIF/%B0%F8%B0%A8%C0%CC%B8%F0%C6%BC%C4%DC.gif?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141201_286/saakrang80_14174402228828oct9_PNG/%BF%C0%B4%C3%C0%C7%C5%BE199.PNG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141201_11/saakrang80_1417413817509lBEoz_PNG/%BE%C6%B8%B6%B7%CE%B4%C